               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390513-name-734" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-734" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-734" type="surname" value="WATSON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-734" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS WATSON</persName>
                  </hi> I am shopman to Mr. Francis Bartholomew, of Fleet-street. on the 11th of May the prisoner came to the shop, and im<lb></lb>mediately stole a bundle of trowsers that were lashed down to the side counter—he broke the cord asunder, and ran off—he dropped some of them—my employer picked up two pairs on the pavement, just outside the door—I ran after the prisoner, he was stopped with the property—he gave five pairs into my arms—these are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390513-name-735" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-735" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
