                        <interp inst="t18390513-name-735" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY BAILEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City police-constable, No</hi> 169.) I saw the prisoner in Water-lane—there was a cry, and I stopped him—he had these trowsers.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi> I left the House of Correction—I was destitute of friends and money—all that night I wandered about, and the next morn<lb></lb>ing I pawned the silk handkerchief off my neck, on that I lived till that day, and then I was forced to do what I did—my character is lost through my own folly undoubtedly.</p>
